{{! views/auth/signup.hbs }}

<div id="form">
  <h2>Signup</h2>
  {{! The HTML formâ€™s action attribute defines where to send the form data when a form is submitted. This and the method="POST" tell us that we should create a post route that will handle the form data. }}
  <form action="/signup" method="POST">

    <label>
      Username
      <input type="text" name="username" />
    </label>

    <label>
      Password
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="********" />
    </label>

    <button type="submit">Create account</button>

    {{! error message will be added here }}
  </form>
</div>